wmsLayer.title: GA0325 D 10m
wmsLayer.description: This layer is a bathymetry grid of survey area D from marine surveys GA0322 and GA0325, collected over the Bonaparte Gulf, north of the Northern Territory. A total of four areas were surveyed and gridded at ten metre resolution. The colour ramp for the WMS is stretched between 30-150 metres water depth. The dataset can be downloaded at the following URL http://services.ga.gov.au/metadata-gateway/metadata/record/76400.
